reviews.review_description:
Everyone and every thing is so cute and standing in front of me!  My favorite stage is the one with the mushrooms and because Diana cheers me on. It's also so great to meet everyone as your own character.  
I haven't finished playing because I'm upgrading my broom right now but I can't wait to see the rest!

One thing is that I wish I could set the voices to Japanese and leave the menus in English.  I wanna hear Hiyocchan's voice but can't read Japanese ^^;
